title: Ravi Singh  - Fresh Off the Boat and Smellin' Like Bombay (vol.
description:
New instrumental mixtape by Ravi Singh!!  As promised, this time it's all old school Bollywood breaks.  The title doesn't refer to any smell or anything like that, just the feeling and idea of being a fish out of water, someplace new and unfamiliar.  We all have had that experience whether it's a new country, a new state, a new city or whatever.  The skits are all skits that both people of Indian origin and non-Indian origin can laugh @ & find humor in.  As usual tho, it's beats for the head, for flowing or whatever you do with your beats!
